title: Argentina in World Cup Final Gives Tired Nation a Reason to Celebrate
description: Hit hard by economic stagnation and inflation, Argentines put hardship aside to watch Lionel Messi and their team take on France and celebrate.

title: Part of 2019 Green Vault Heist Loot Recovered in Berlin
description: The surrender of some stolen pieces came after talks between prosecutors and lawyers for the men charged with the theft.

title: Ukraine Races to Restore Power in Cities After Russian Missile Barrage
description: Russian assaults are eroding Ukrainians’ access to heat, light and water as temperatures drop.

title: Putin's New Strategy: Laying Claim to Traditional Values
description: Searching for allies against Ukraine, Russia now presents itself as the leader of a global culture war against moral depravity. It’s not working.
